headline: Wall Street Analysts Believe Epam (EPAM) Could Rally 26.37%: Here's is How to Trade
summary: The average of price targets set by Wall Street analysts indicates a potential upside of 26.4% in Epam (EPAM). While the effectiveness of this highly sought-after metric is questionable, the positive trend in earnings estimate revisions might translate into an upside in the stock.
